      "body": "It is possible to create a `guix environment` without the restriction of containers... I have a branch I've been working on, will resurrect that and see how it works out!\r\n\r\nLooking at an experience close to python's virtualenv:\r\n\r\n```sh\r\n./contrib/guix/env.sh  # builds environment, sets env vars, and execs $SHELL\r\n./autogen.sh\r\n./configure\r\nmake -j\"$(nproc)\" check\r\n# Ctrl-D to exit environment\r\n```",
